title: Earnings Outlook What to watch for in Apple’s earnings
text:
Earnings Outlook: What to watch for in Apple’s earnings 
Market Watch Saturday 24th October, 2015 
Earnings: Analysts expect Apple to report earnings per share of $1.87, up from $1.42 in the year-earlier period. Estimize, a fast-growing software platform that uses crowdsourcing from hedge fund executives, brokerages and analysts to make estimates, has Apple earning slightly more: $1.91 a share. Apple has surpassed the FactSet consensus in the last 11 consecutive fiscal quarters.
